# Omitted:
# test2		"\\tmp" doesn't work.
# test10	'errorformat' is different
# test12	can't unlink a swap file
# test25	uses symbolic link
# test27	can't edit file with "*" in file name
# test97	\{ and \$ are not escaped characters.

